About Me

Nationality: Nigerian/American

My love for computers helped grow my passion for web development. The satisfaction of solving a difficult problem was a reward in and of itself. I define myself by the artistic and functional capabilites I develop in my projects. While skills can be taught, my work ethic and perserverance are two characteristics I pride myself upon.
